.wikiwyg_formatting_test
This is <span style="font-weight: bold;">bold</span> <span style="font-style:
italic;">italic</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">strike</span> <span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: line-through;">mish-mash</span> yo<br>
~~
This is *bold* _italic_ -strike- -*_mish-mash_*- yo
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

.wikiwyg_formatting_test
<a href="/public/index.cgi?shy">burger</a>
~~
[burger]
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

.wikiwyg_formatting_test
<a href="/public/index.cgi?shame"><!-- wiki-renamed-link -->burger</a>
~~
"burger"[shame]
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

.wikiwyg_formatting_test
a &nbsp; b
~~
a b
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

.wikiwyg_formatting_test
<table><tr><td><p>Hey d00d</p></td></tr></table>
~~
| Hey d00d |
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

.wikiwyg_formatting_test
<h2>foo</h2>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<h2>bar</h2>
~~
^^ foo

^^ bar
.wikiwyg_formatting_test

^^^ {rt 14784}
Regardless of what's in the bulleted list item, no blank line should go
between the `* ` line and the `** ` line.
.wikiwyg_formatting_test
<div class="wiki">
<ul>
<li>Get <strong>behind</strong> me</li>

<ul>
<li>Satan!</li>
</ul></ul>
<br/></div>
~~~
* Get *behind* me
** Satan!
.wikiwyg_formatting_test
